00:21:10.851 --> 00:21:14.152
far der milkhome hob ikh zey gezen, fleg ikh forn tsu keyn Varshe.

00:21:14.142 --> 00:21:16.870
s'iz nisht geven vayt fun Kraznitsav?

00:21:16.740 --> 00:21:20.720
s'iz, s'iz, s'iz nisht ge- hundert un fuftsik kilometer, tsi fertsik.

00:21:19.677 --> 00:21:21.898
iz vi azoy zaynt ir geforn dort?

00:21:22.613 --> 00:21:23.586
⟨mit der⟩ ban.

00:21:24.418 --> 00:21:26.217
⟨P- in⟩ Poyln iz geven a ban.

00:21:28.047 --> 00:21:30.370
un vos gedenkt ir fun zey?

00:21:31.354 --> 00:21:33.002
s'iz geven a groyse mishpokhe,

00:21:33.936 --> 00:21:36.960
geven a por hundert mentshn in Varshe, mishpokhe.

00:21:35.792 --> 00:21:36.781
emes?

00:21:38.222 --> 00:21:40.528
zaynen zey geblibn nokh di milkhome lebn?

00:21:41.470 --> 00:21:43.464
g- ikh aleyn bin geblibn lebn.

00:21:45.698 --> 00:21:47.312
vos nokh vilt ir mir zogn?

00:21:48.010 --> 00:21:49.840
vos nokh, mishpokhe...

00:21:50.980 --> 00:21:54.383
vos ir vilt mir zogn vegn di, vegn ayer tsayt

00:21:54.422 --> 00:21:55.783
in, in,

00:21:55.873 --> 00:21:58.837
Kraznitsav tsi in, in, in Sibir.

00:21:59.164 --> 00:22:01.440
vos vilt ir mir dertseyln?

00:22:00.160 --> 00:22:02.246
 kh'hob, kh'hob shoyn, dakht zikh, alts.

00:22:06.876 --> 00:22:10.548
'KAY. kh'vil aykh zeyer badanken far dem intervyu,

00:22:10.572 --> 00:22:11.561
OKAY.

00:22:10.690 --> 00:22:12.321
zeyer a sheynem dank.

00:22:13.288 --> 00:22:14.598
zayt mir gezunt.

00:22:14.537 --> 00:22:16.170
ir zayt oykh gezunt.

00:22:21.709 --> 00:22:24.020
Meyer, zayt azoy gut

00:22:22.587 --> 00:22:23.475
UNK

00:22:24.020 --> 00:22:27.592
un dertseylt mir, ver iz di sheyne froy vos zitst lebn aykh yetst?

00:22:28.071 --> 00:22:31.625
lebn mir zitst di shenste un di kligste.

00:22:32.948 --> 00:22:35.389
yo, un ver iz zi, di kligste?

00:22:35.850 --> 00:22:36.755
mayn vayb.

00:22:36.981 --> 00:22:38.797
un vi lang zaynt ir farheyrat?

00:22:38.685 --> 00:22:40.740
eyn un fuftsik yor UNK.

00:22:39.985 --> 00:22:41.177
keyn eynhore!

00:22:41.622 --> 00:22:43.134
un vos vilt ir zogn?

00:22:43.697 --> 00:22:44.630
eyn zakh.

00:22:44.630 --> 00:22:46.509
zogt mir epes vegn ayer froy.

00:22:49.401 --> 00:22:51.994
ir hot shoyn gezogt az zi iz di kligste. vos nokh?

00:23:03.120 --> 00:23:04.312
⟨vos, vos zogt men?⟩

00:23:03.812 --> 00:23:08.159
ir hot mir shoyn gezogt az zi iz di kligste, iz kent ir mir yetst zogn az zi iz di shenste oykhet.

00:23:07.491 --> 00:23:09.110
⟨, di⟩ shenste oykhet.

00:23:08.453 --> 00:23:11.197
OKAY. a sheynem dank!

00:23:14.930 --> 00:23:15.770
GOOD.

00:23:19.303 --> 00:23:21.372
Meyer, ver iz dos?

00:23:20.110 --> 00:23:20.660
yo.

00:23:21.632 --> 00:23:24.360
dos iz finef khaveyrim,

00:23:24.850 --> 00:23:27.313
hobn balangt tsum kibuts in Lide.

00:23:28.348 --> 00:23:29.692
un vu zaynt ir?

00:23:32.415 --> 00:23:33.927
d- dort ⟨azoy...⟩

00:23:33.428 --> 00:23:34.434
in mitl?

00:23:34.255 --> 00:23:36.409
⟨n-⟩ yo, in MIDDLE, ⟨der, dray⟩.

00:23:36.330 --> 00:23:38.906
un ven iz dos, ven hot men dos genumen?

00:23:39.013 --> 00:23:41.201
dos hot men genumen in zeks un draysikstn yor.

00:23:40.515 --> 00:23:41.994
in zeks un draysik.

00:23:46.354 --> 00:23:48.018
Meyer, ver iz dos?

00:23:49.307 --> 00:23:50.280
v- ver?

00:23:51.113 --> 00:23:52.288
ver iz dos?

00:23:52.243 --> 00:23:54.076
d- dos iz mayn shvester.

00:23:53.577 --> 00:23:55.073
vos iz ir nomen?

00:23:55.078 --> 00:23:56.034
Khane.

00:23:56.614 --> 00:23:58.295
un vu iz dos genumen?

00:23:59.398 --> 00:24:01.957
d- dos ho- dos ⟨ho⟩⟨UNK⟩ genumen in Poyln.

00:24:02.335 --> 00:24:04.084
in velekhe yor, gedenkt ir?

00:24:04.178 --> 00:24:05.660
kh'ken nisht gedenken.

00:24:06.064 --> 00:24:08.505
in Ulm. UNK geven krank, bin ikh geven.

00:24:09.355 --> 00:24:10.733
ver iz dos?

00:24:10.620 --> 00:24:11.728
dos bin ikh.

00:24:11.802 --> 00:24:14.830
un ven iz dos genumen?

00:24:14.788 --> 00:24:16.503
dos iz genumen in Daytshland.

00:24:16.628 --> 00:24:17.854
velekhe shtot?

00:24:17.927 --> 00:24:18.748
Ulm.

00:24:20.190 --> 00:24:22.646
, ir gedenkt velekhe yor?

00:24:23.412 --> 00:24:25.313
UNK gedenk ⟨shoyn⟩ nisht UNK.

00:24:28.643 --> 00:24:30.390
in nayntsn nayn un fertsik?

